    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine starts reliably, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. However, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, and the air conditioning takes a few minutes to get cold. It is a solid, honest car that has been maintained regularly but definitely shows signs of its years on the road.",
