      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, an exemplary choice for the discerning driver. Demonstrating a commitment to mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement, this motorcar offers a sophisticated driving experience characterized by reliable performance and a well-appointed interior. Its comprehensive service history underscores a legacy of attentive ownership, ensuring it meets the high standards expected of our curated inventory. We invite you to inspect this distinguished model and appreciate its enduring quality firsthand.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
